{"tid":1281822,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母呻完想自殺未","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:17:12.000Z","uid":52962,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe102602bb22e838dba71ae0d30068123f7d09f","tid":1281822,"uid":52962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"你明知對抗嘅係一大個政治機器<br />\n你哋對抗嘅係一班有財有勢有武器嘅高端社會老人<br />\n你地唔係認為由6月12號到今時今日兩個星期就可以得到完全勝利下話<br />\n<br />\n出邊有兄弟姊妹衝緊，有和理非流緊汗<br />\n你幾條撚樣就喺度呻要自殺，令到各位兄弟姊妹本來已經非常疲勞仲要顧及你嘅生死，撲到個閪咁走去搵你<br />\n令本來唔夠瞓嗰幾位議員，好似湊仔咁湊你<br />\n屌你老味你知唔知係俾麻煩自己人，令到自己人更加灰心<br />\n屌你老味你知唔知你令仇恨我哋嘅人更加開心更加鼓舞<br />\n<br />\n火都嚟"},{"pid":"5419bcd32ed385d6b1e149c39ef7c674e2c04759","tid":1281822,"uid":154223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"今日同成班巴絲淋住雨去搵人，一個二個樣殘到，根本未抖夠又扑出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再要我地擔心啦"},{"pid":"185a849a721306bb3248a18bd75a8c307f2562f9","tid":1281822,"uid":78349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"一個月都堅持唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就嗌死"},{"pid":"d6bfb32d5bf8efe78badc84673454c3d82b2920f","tid":1281822,"uid":104502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"attention seeker"},{"pid":"70bc6406c56050670fbfd73a903771ff63fe2dd7","tid":1281822,"uid":52962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"185a849a721306bb3248a18bd75a8c307f2562f9","tid":1281822,"uid":78349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"一個月都堅持唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\